      *             Reference Rate and confirms if valid.             *
      *                                                               *
      *  (c) Finastra International Limited 2006                      *
      *                                                               *
      *  Last Amend No. EML112             Date 23Feb21               *
      *  Prev Amend No. MD057558           Date 18Feb21               *
      *                 MD057049           Date 03Nov20               *
