      *             separator in the Dealing ICD was defined as ","   *
      *             instead of ".".                                   *
      *  CSF011A - CCR015: Display Order in Confirmation Pages        *
      *            (Recompile)                                        *
      *  CRE073 - Interest Rate Rounding (Recompile)                  *
      *  CDL049 - Addition of a Reference Rate field                  *
