      * Incoming Transaction
     D TranInPrim    E DS                  EXTNAME(MMLDNIPD)

      * First DS for access programs, short data structure
     D DSFDY         E DS                  EXTNAME(DSFDY)

      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ Named constants                      ¦
      ** ¦ ===============                      ¦
      ** +--------------------------------------+

      ** +--------------------------------------+
      ** ¦ Declared variables                   ¦
      ** ¦ ==================                   ¦
